product.description: SanDisk Ultra microSDXC and microSDHC cards are fast for better pictures, app performance, and Full HD video. Ideal for Android smartphones and tablets, these A1-rated cards load apps faster for a better smartphone experience. Available in capacities up to 400GB, you have the capacity to take more pictures and Full HD video and capture life at its fullest. Built to perform in harsh conditions, SanDisk Ultra microSD cards are waterproof, temperature proof, shockproof, and X-ray proof. The microSD card is also rated Class 10 for Full HD video recording performance and a 10-year limited warranty. 1GB=1,000,000,000 bytes. Actual user storage less.
